sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant U as User
    participant F as React PWA
    participant G as Nginx Gateway
    participant BS as Budget Service
    participant DS as Debt Service
    participant AIS as AI Agent Service
    participant PG as PostgreSQL
    participant AO as Azure OpenAI

    rect rgb(230,250,230)
    Note over U,PG: Flow 1: Expense Entry
    U->>F: Enter expense ₹500 Food
    F->>F: Validate input
    F->>G: POST /expenses (with JWT)
    G->>G: Verify JWT + Rate limit
    G->>BS: Forward request
    BS->>PG: INSERT expense
    BS->>PG: UPDATE budgets
    BS-->>G: 201 Created
    G-->>F: Success response
    F-->>U: Show updated dashboard
    end

    rect rgb(230,240,255)
    Note over U,AO: Flow 2: AI Question
    U->>F: Ask: How can I save more?
    F->>G: POST /agents/chat
    G->>AIS: Forward question
    AIS->>PG: Fetch user expenses + budgets
    AIS->>PG: Query financial_concepts (pgvector)
    AIS->>AO: Send prompt with context
    AO-->>AIS: LLM response
    AIS->>PG: Log interaction
    AIS-->>G: Formatted answer
    G-->>F: JSON response
    F-->>U: Display AI answer
    end

    rect rgb(255,245,230)
    Note over U,PG: Flow 3: Weekly Report
    U->>F: Click Generate Weekly Report
    F->>G: GET /agents/reports/weekly
    G->>AIS: Forward request
    AIS->>BS: MCP call: analyze_spending
    BS-->>AIS: Spending analysis
    AIS->>DS: MCP call: calculate_payoff_plan
    DS-->>AIS: Debt analysis
    AIS->>PG: Store report
    AIS-->>G: Report JSON
    G-->>F: Report data
    F-->>U: Render report view
    end
